	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 highlander-comment" id="li-comment-259753">
		<article id="comment-259753" class="contain">
			<footer class="comment-meta contain vcard">

				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1c9c2b1b4836126b4577083eb7898367?s=40&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40' height='40' width='40' />
				<div class="comment-author">
				<span class="fn">Kim, JungWon (2012621820)</span> on <a href="http://hklawblog.com/2014/10/03/illegal-organ-trade-in-china/comment-page-1/#comment-259753"><time pubdate datetime="2014-10-07T20:32:34+00:00">October 7, 2014 at 8:32 PM</time></a> said:
									</div><!-- .comment-author -->

				
			</footer><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content"><p>Thanks for the sharing Wing Yee. </p>
<p>I&#8217;ve always been interested in this topic of organ tradings in China. I value and appreciate your argument that trading human organ is unethical and legalizing the trading of organs would lead to black markets emerging and more active transactions. The reasons you have stated behind this argument is valid and I see the logic however I also expect that leaving the trading of organs illegal would also create black markets, if not drive it more active due to high demand. </p>
<p> Regardless of the legalization, if the strong demand is present and remains, the practice would exist and grow in market. This means that if this procedure is not legalized, all these procedures would not be authorized. And as you stated, unauthorized transplant would be highly dangerous. </p>
<p> My suggestion is that despite such trading action is immoral and unethical, for the sake of the welfare of the donor and the patient, the trading should be legalized with attached stringent legislation such as strict criteria of the practitioner or the doctor.</p>
</div>

			<div class="reply contain">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2014/10/03/illegal-organ-trade-in-china/?replytocom=259753#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "comment-259753", "259753", "respond", "3249" )' aria-label='Reply to Kim, JungWon (2012621820)'>Reply</a>			</div><!-- .reply -->
